Class MapImporter

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.ehri.project.importers.base.AbstractImporter<Map<String,Object>>
      • eu.ehri.project.importers.base.MapImporter
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    CsvAuthoritativeItemImporter, PersonalitiesImporter, SaxXmlImporter, UkrainianUnitImporter, Wp2PersonalitiesImporter

    public abstract class MapImporter
extends AbstractImporter<Map<String,Object>>
    Importer of Map based representations of documentary units, historical agents, virtual collections and other entities. Does not implement the actual import methods.
